title: James Brown Live In Berlin 1988 DVDRip x264 aac 5.1 mp4
description:
JAMES BROWN LIVE IN BERLIN (1988)

The Godfather of Soul played this concert in Berlin at an
interesting stage in his career, just after his huge 
international hit Living In America, and before his
rediscovery through sampling as the 80s became the 90s.
Many of his classics are here; presented with effortless 
showmanship and aplomb, offering a rare opportunity to take
a ringside seat and watch the legendary Soul Brother Number
One James Brown at close quarters.
